"TONNEX 1-0", a date code of '''0110''', "94V-0", "38G4069A", and '''MultiTech''''s text (below) is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :<small>"MultiTech Systems", "JOE.H", "AGS:200103 Ver. 0"<??>, "Broandband Router LAN Wireless" This router would seem to be identical to the [[Argus Technologies EW-2101]].
10Mbit WAN, 100Mbit LAN
The power supply shown in the FCC photos is a '''High Power''' HPW-1009U (100-240VAC ~ 50-60Hz, 1.0A max. -> 9VDC, 1.1A).
